call:
Shayela_0_
Usesha ifayela ngegama, futhi uthayiphe ngokuzithandela, kufolda elinikeziwe, noma kusuka ku-CWD, ngokuphindaphindeka uye ezansi bese uya phezulu,
Futhi uyilayishe ngokuya ngohlobo lwayo ngokuzenzakalelayo.

{version}: Igama lesisekelo sefayela, ngaphandle kokunwetshwa.
    Thayipha{description}: Ukunwetshwa okulindelekile{modules_list}.
    indlela{function_count}: Indlela yokuqala yokusesha kusuka.
    I-Timeout(...): Isikhathi sokucinga esiphezulu ngemizuzwana.
    Î ent(bool, optional): Uma kuyiqiniso, kuphakamisa iphutha uma amafayela amaningi anegama elifanayo atholakala.)

IMITHEMBISO: okuqukethwe kwefayela elitholakele noma alikho.
load_user_translations:
Layisha_user_translations{package}
Ilayisha ukuhumusha okuchazwe ngumsebenzisi kusuka kufayela le-{version} futhi lizihlanganise ngokuhumusha okuzenzakalelayo.

Amapharamitha:
    I-Lang_Path{description}: Indlela eya kwifayela lokuhumusha lomsebenzisi. Okuzenzakalelayo ku- "lang.{modules_list}".

Ukuziphatha:
    - Uma ifayela likhona futhi livumelekile{function_count}, lihlanganisa okuqukethwe kwalo ngezinguqulo ezenzakalelayo
    - Uma ifayela lingekho, ligcina ukuhumusha okuzenzakalelayo kuphela
    - Ibonisa i-popup yesexwayiso uma ifayela likhona kepha alikwazi ukulayishwa
    - Ivuselela isichazamazwi somhlaba jikelele _franslations

Qaphela: Lo msebenzi kufanele ubizwe ngaphambi kokusebenzisa i-T () umsebenzi wokuhumusha abasebenzisi ukuze usebenze.
switch:
Uhlelo oluthuthukisiwe lwe-switchch-case for{package}. Usekela:
- Izikhiye eziningi ezifanayo ngecala ngalinye
- Qondanisa ngenani, uhlobo, i-regex, umsebenzi we-lambda, noma isigaba
- Ama-Pandas kanye Numpy Data Hlela Ukusekelwa
- Ukungenziwa kwe-Async kwamacala
- Umdlalo-yonke imodi yokwenza amacala amaningi afanayo
- Imodi ye-Debug ukuze ungene kumacala wokufanisa
async_switch:
Wrapper to Instant switch in mode async. Amapharamitha:
- Inani: inani lokufanisa namacala achaziwe.
- ** KwaRgs: Izimpikiswano ezingukhiye ongazikhethela zidluliselwe ngqo ekilasini lokushintsha. Lokhu kungafaka:
  - Match_All{package}: Yenza wonke amacala afanayo esikhundleni sokuma ekuqaleni.
  - Debug{version}: Phrinta yiliphi icala elifaniswe nokuthi yini eyenziwe.
  - I-Async_mode{description}: Akufanele iphasiswe ngesandla lapha{modules_list}.
Isibonelo: asyncwitch{function_count}(...)
